                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Also something to keep in mind, is that Stasis isn't a spell, and therefore doesn't need to wait on spell gem refresh (2.25 seconds).
<br />

<br />
To mez 2 mobs with spells takes 7.25 seconds.
<br />
(2.5s cast + 2.25s refresh +2.5s cast)
<br />

<br />
However, you can use Stasis during that refresh time, if it time is a critical factor.
<br />
(2.5s cast + 1.5s activation + .75s left on refresh +2.5s cast)
<br />

<br />
First rank is definately worth the cost.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=378985" target="_blank" class="postlink">Master Tashim</a>
<br />
<a href="http://www.botsguild.org/" target="_blank" class="postlink">Brotherhood of the Spider</a></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
